<P>SOME Select Ca&s;es RESOLVED. Specially, tending to the <HI>right Ordering</HI> of <HI>the Heart,</HI> that we may <HI>comfortably walk with God</HI> in our <HI>general</HI> and <HI>par|ticular Callings:</HI> &amp;c.</P>
