<P>By THOMAS SHEPARD, M. A. Formerly of <HI>Emmanuel-College</HI> in <HI>Cambridge</HI> in <HI>England:</HI> Afterward Mini&s;ter of <HI>Cambridge</HI> in <HI>New-England.</HI></P>
